room_title: Escape room "Hostage" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: This was our first time going to Breakout and w head an amazing time. We did the hostage room and surprisingly we finished the room with 7 minutes left. Our game master was very friendly and helpful. I'm most definitely going to go back and try some other rooms because it was so much fun. Go check these rooms out you won't be dissapoint

room_title: Escape room "Hostage" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: I did the Hostage room and it was really fun and I had a great time. Lexi was my game master and she was awesome.!!!

room_title: Escape room "Hostage" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: Highly recommend Breakout for fun family bonding time. This was our first time doing an escape room. We chose the hostage room which was one of their more challenges games. We look forward to going back. Abdul was a wonderful game host.

room_title: Escape room "Hostage" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: Visiting Memphis for the first time and loved Breakout!!! The Hostage room was super fun. We also had the best game masters Gabe and Chase!!!! Thanks for the experience- we will be back!!!!

room_title: Escape room "Hostage" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: Awesome experience.. staff was awesome as well! Definitely going again soon! Gotta try them all!
